ent-CMPortableSurgicalBed-name = portable surgical bed
ent-CMPortableSurgicalBed-desc = A collapsible surgical bed. It's not perfect, but it's the best you'll get short of an actual surgical table.
ent-RMCMedevacStretcher-name = medevac stretcher
ent-RMCMedevacStretcher-desc = A collapsible stretcher that can be activated to send patients to an overhead dropship.
ent-RMCRollerBedHospital-name = hospital roller bed
ent-RMCRollerBedHospital-desc = A basic cushioned leather board resting on a small frame. Not very comfortable at all, but allows the patient to rest lying down while moved to another location rapidly. Not great for surgery, but better than nothing.
